Sentencas: Pr0.8Sr0.2Fe0.8Ni0.2O3-delta (PN22) films have been deposited at different temperatures on yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ) substrates by pulsed laser deposition (PLD) for application to thin film solid oxide fuel cell cathodes.
Titulo: Structural and electrical properties of thin films of Pr0.8Sr0.2Fe0.8Ni0.2O3-δ

Sentencas: The structure of the films was analysed by X-ray diffraction (XRD) and atomic force microscopy (AFM).
Titulo: Structural and electrical properties of thin films of Pr0.8Sr0.2Fe0.8Ni0.2O3-δ

Sentencas: A marked influence in the structural properties of the substrate temperature has been found but not of the composition.
Titulo: Structural and electrical properties of thin films of Pr0.8Sr0.2Fe0.8Ni0.2O3-δ

Sentencas: Samples deposited at temperatures below 700 degrees C are amorphous, with granular aspect, and with decreasing roughness with the temperature.
Titulo: Structural and electrical properties of thin films of Pr0.8Sr0.2Fe0.8Ni0.2O3-δ

Sentencas: Meanwhile, the films at 700 degrees C are polycrystalline and exhibit a needle-shaped surface, with the highest roughness observed.
Titulo: Structural and electrical properties of thin films of Pr0.8Sr0.2Fe0.8Ni0.2O3-δ

Sentencas: Additionally, the conducting behaviour of the films has been studied by electrochemical impedance spectroscopy (EIS) and their cathodic area specific resistance (ASR) was determined.
Titulo: Structural and electrical properties of thin films of Pr0.8Sr0.2Fe0.8Ni0.2O3-δ

Sentencas: The main part of the impedance of the testing cells is due to the electrode.
Titulo: Structural and electrical properties of thin films of Pr0.8Sr0.2Fe0.8Ni0.2O3-δ

Sentencas: The ASR values of the films of PN22 are lower than those of Pr0.9Sr0.1Fe0.8Ni0.2O3-delta (PN12), being the lowest 0.5 Omega cm(2) at 850 degrees C for the sample PN22 deposited at room temperature.
Titulo: Structural and electrical properties of thin films of Pr0.8Sr0.2Fe0.8Ni0.2O3-δ
